{"tid":1860221,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士司機開咪叫大家帶口罩","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:56:39.000Z","uid":7737,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8e8539ec64a7db9b75e7403613a90f3747bddf","tid":1860221,"uid":7737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 無錄到音 因為無諗過司機會開咪講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係好想表揚呢位司機 所以先開post同大家share下<br />\n<br />\n事發係：<br />\n我係由總站上車 架巴士開左無耐 司機就開咪同大家講：<br />\n各位乘客，為左家人及自己著想 請佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我睇唔到有無人真係因為咁而帶返個罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢一個moment <br />\n我都覺得大家真係connected 大家都齊心抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且巴士司機真係個高風險職業 <br />\n日本都有單旅遊巴士司機載武漢團中左招<br />\n如果咁多位司機都企硬要乘客帶罩 真係會有助減低社會感染嘅風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時少打文 sry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aff785a46656896d2fd739649d99ec7fee0f573","tid":1860221,"uid":267909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"上之開咪叫癈老關收音機<br />\n要聽帶head phone"},{"pid":"1948a875b92cc6c56a34914f3abb9f3e3b042d4c","tid":1860221,"uid":7737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aff785a46656896d2fd739649d99ec7fee0f573","tid":1860221,"uid":267909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"上之開咪叫癈老關收音機<br />\n要聽帶head phone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"我今次第一次聽司機開mic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽到佢咁講真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea1b4577ea08d23553825e40fc8b0382656c3f7","tid":1860221,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aff785a46656896d2fd739649d99ec7fee0f573","tid":1860221,"uid":267909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"上之開咪叫癈老關收音機<br />\n要聽帶head phone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"好正喎"},{"pid":"30ccac4d2f74f39efdd91ae03c274c989f78efe1","tid":1860221,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"be4892b101964a569c9bbf6c143f6837379834e2","tid":1860221,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"家陣係買唔到口罩呀<br />\n<br />\n巴士司機 開咪屌鳩林鄭啦"}]}